data.description: Located in Stone Bay Plantation, this updated three bedroom home is in a very desirable location.  Upon entering this home, the dining room is located to the right, which passes through to the kitchen with an eating area, white cabinetry, quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances.  The open family room looks out over the wooded rear yard and deck.  Two bedrooms and a full bath are towards the front of the home, and the owner's suite with bath is located on the other side of the home.  A bonus room is located over the garage area.  Beautifully maintained home, just a 10 minute drive to N Topsail Beach!  Very close to Camp Lejuene's rear gate, and easy travel to Wilmington and Jacksonville. Note:  Propane fireplace has been disconnected.
